Package: cl-ltk
Version: 0.8.7
Revision: 1
Description: Common Lisp binding for the Tk toolkit
License: LGPL
Maintainer: Lars Rosengreen <lars@margay.org>

Type: cl

Depends: clc, clisp-clc | cmucl-clc | openmcl-clc | sbcl-clc, tcltk

Source: http://www.peter-herth.de/ltk/ltk-%v.tgz
Source-MD5: c1d2ec2bd84f7a5a2fbf289bd6427d4f

SourceDirectory: ltk

PatchScript: sed 's|@PREFIX@|%p|g' <%a/cl-ltk.patch | patch -p1

CompileScript: /usr/bin/true

InstallScript: <<
  find . -type d -exec chmod 755 {} \;
  find . -type f -exec chmod 644 {} \;
  mkdir -p %i/share/common-lisp/source/ltk
  cp -Rp * %i/share/common-lisp/source/ltk
  mkdir -p %i/share/common-lisp/systems
  ln -s %p/share/common-lisp/source/ltk/ltk.asd %i/share/common-lisp/systems/ltk.asd
<<

PostInstScript: %p/sbin/register-common-lisp-source ltk
PreRmScript: %p/sbin/unregister-common-lisp-source ltk

DescDetail: << 
Provides support for creating graphical user interfaces in Common Lisp
using Tk.
<<

DescUsage: <<
(asdf:oos 'asdf:load-op 'ltk)
<<

Homepage: http://www.peter-herth.de/ltk/

